creting CV at the given orbital period. Objects like V405 Peg might represent\nthe tip of an iceberg and thus may be important contributors to the Galactic\nRidge X-ray Emission. If so they will be uncovered by future X-ray surveys,\ne.g. with eROSITA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2013 16:33:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
