\ndedicated observations of faint galaxies in the rest-frame UV, in order to\nbetter determine their physical properties. Observed escape fractions outside\nour proposed range bear relevant consequences on the nature of the\nastrophysical sources responsible for cosmic reionization and/or its buildup\nprocess.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2013 21:00:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
